# Organization And Personnel Management

# Search to get all department data

Get all department data

HTTP Request

GET http://[server]/jsf/rfws/emp/deptType/getDeptData

Parameters

Name Type Description
No Parameters needed

Result (in JSON Array)

Name Type Description
size int Size of JsonArray in values
values string Data, depends on Table
name string Name. Empty
fields string Field Details

Sample request:

OkHttpClient client = new OkHttpClient();

String url = "http://" + server + "/jsf/rfws/emp/deptType/getDeptData";

Request request = new Request.Builder()
  .url(url)
  .get()
  .addHeader("client_id", clientID)
  .addHeader("authorization", "Bearer " + token)
  .addHeader("cache-control", "no-cache")
  .build();

Response response = client.newCall(request).execute();

# Search to get all department data

Get all department data

HTTP Request

GET http://[server]/jsf/rfws/emp/deptType/getDeptData

Parameters

Name Type Description
deptId integer The department ID

Result (in JSON Array)

Name Type Description
size int Size of JsonArray in values
values string Data, depends on Table
name string Name. Empty
fields string Field Details

OkHttpClient client = new OkHttpClient();

# Get a list of employee's Basic Info.

HTTP Request

GET http://[server]/jsf/rfws/emp/termination/getEmpNoticeRequired

Parameters

Name Type Description
empId String(Query) Required. ID of terminated Employee
effDate String(Query) Required. Date String of Employee Termination Effective Date

Result (in JSON Array)

Name Type Description
size int Size of JsonArray in values
values string Data, depends on Table
name string Name. Empty
fields string Field Details

Sample request:

OkHttpClient client = new OkHttpClient();

String url = "http://" + server + "/jsf/rfws/emp/termination/getEmpNoticeRequired?empId=" + empId & effDate=" + effDate;

Request request = new Request.Builder()
  .url(url)
  .get()
  .addHeader("client_id", clientID)
  .addHeader("authorization", "Bearer " + token)
  .addHeader("cache-control", "no-cache")
